        {
            "title": "粉嶺公路淡水管爆裂  多車被沙石擊中",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"路邊噴出大瀑布。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7137b6ffbb66ee91d7f70022c1e411b6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040511440137433.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">路邊噴出大瀑布。fb：馬路的事討論區</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（5日）晨10時許，粉嶺公路往元朗方向近和合石對開工地，疑工人掘路時敲爆淡水管，形成大噴泉，泥沙夾雜石頭激射而出，擊中駛經車輛，警方接獲多宗投訴，通知水務署及路政署跟進，受事故影響，來回四條線一度全封。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177995/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"路邊噴出大瀑布。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4cb473be63e8c5d0d792ba0c6b967662/2025-04/01.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        路邊噴出大瀑布。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177996/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"路邊噴出大瀑布。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aefc327a40885a6e29426fe69d0f5540/2025-04/02.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">