            "title": "將軍澳廢物回收場男工人被機器夾傷手 清醒送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"男工人被夾傷手清醒送院治理。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/05c8c9a0ac9eafcbc06ae45ddae1ae4f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040511285838333.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">男工人被夾傷手清醒送院治理。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>將軍澳工業邨駿昌街8號，今（5日）早上10時30分，一個廢物回收環保工場，一名50多歲男工人使用機器工作期間，意外被機器夾住手指，動彈不得，工友見狀報警求助，救援人員到場為他解困，他左手虎口位被夾傷，清醒送往將軍澳醫院治理，警方列工業意外，由相關部門跟進調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177972/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男工人清醒送院治理。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2ef45679eef202c2aaad83b155ac827/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_112355767.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男工人清醒送院治理。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
